\"></div>\n\n    <header>\n      <div class=\"shell nav\">\n        <a class=\"brand\" href=\"/\">Rox dT</a>\n        <nav class=\"nav-links\" aria-label=\"Primary\">\n          <a href=\"#projects\">Projects</a>\n          <a href=\"#focus\">Focus</a>\n          <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n          <a href=\"https://github.com/rxdt\">GitHub</a>\n        </nav>\n      </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <main>\n      <div class=\"shell hero\">\n        <div class=\"hero-copy\">\n          <div class=\"eyebrow\">Loop Engineer in San Francisco</div>\n          <h1>\n            Human in the loop. All about tech that has to survive first contact.\n          </h1>\n          <p class=\"lede\">\n            I did my time at FAANGs as a SWE and FDE / Partner Engineer, then a\n            stint in VC. Some stealthy startup time. Now I build apps with my AI\n            interns, with a lot of verification (renmants of my time in DevEx).\n          </p>\n          <div class=\"actions\" role=\"group\" aria-label=\"Primary links\">\n            <a class=\"button\" href=\"https://github.com/rxdt/loopgate-harness\"\n              >Python LoopGate Harness</a\n            >\n            <a\n              class=\"button secondary\"\n              href=\"https://github.com/rxdt/loopgate_js\"\n              >Frontend LoopGate Harness</a\n            >\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <figure class=\"portrait\">\n          <img src=\"/assets/merged.gif\" alt=\"Animated portrait of Rox dT\" />\n        </figure>\n      </div>\n\n      <section id=\"projects\">\n        <div class=\"shell\">\n          <div class=\"section-head\">\n            <h2>Recent Projects</h2>\n          </div>\n          <div class=\"project-grid\">\n            <article class=\"project\">\n              <a\n                class=\"project-media\"\n                href=\"https://aideploymentcalculator.vercel.app/\"\n                aria-label=\"Open the AI Deployment Calculator\"\n              >\n  