checks pass\\n3. Tests are written to cover code 100%\\n4. Lighthouse and Playwright pass 100%\\n5. All checks pass\\n6. All work in `frontend/specs` is complete\\n7. The owner verifies manually the site 'looks' right locally\\n8. The owner deploys the app to the site\\n\\n## Out of Scope\\n\\nCreating a backend app\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_3\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/zsh -c 'rg --files docs/specs docs | sort'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":null,\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_3\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/zsh -c 'rg --files docs/specs docs | sort'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"docs/PROJECT_STATUS.md\\ndocs/PROMPT.md\\ndocs/plan.md\\ndocs/specs/frontend.md\\ndocs/specs/frontend.md\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_4\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/zsh -c 'git status --short'\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":null,\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_4\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/zsh -c 'git status --short'\",\"aggregated_output\":\" M harness/cli.ts\\n M harness/ralph.sh\\n\",\"exit_code\":0,\"status\":\"completed\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_5\",\"type\":\"agent_message\",\"text\":\"There are pre-existing edits in forbidden `harness/` files; I’ll leave them untouched and only stage relevant work later. Next I’m reading the frontend spec and repo structure.\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.started\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_6\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"/bin/zsh -c \\\"sed -n '1,240p' docs/specs/frontend.md\\\"\",\"aggregated_output\":\"\",\"exit_code\":null,\"status\":\"in_progress\"}}\n{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_6\",\"type\":\"command_execution\",\"command\":\"